{"tid":1544253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［跳閘］屌你老母放爆","createTime":"2019-09-05T13:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T16:42:56.000Z","uid":202580,"like":143,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"e73eb3e7b5e05a76c878479fe15a589747cd078b","tid":1544253,"uid":202580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:20:00.000Z","msg":"從九月起我喺黨鐵打工，着住件粉紅色蛤蚧衣捉人跳閘，而我捉人嘅原則係：「屌你老母放爆」<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，就係屌你老母放爆，老子先唔會理公司蝕錢啲乜春嘢，每次見人跳閘我都唔撚理。當有Ching助跑時我喺隔離吶喊助威，睇到啲淆底獸喺閘前徘徊我仲屌佢快撚啲跳。見到有人拉大隊一齊跳閘，我直頭開職員通道費事煩，真係你阿媽大減價。<br />\n<br />\n我仲記得，喺我返工嘅第三日，站長跑嚟同我講，呢兩日車資收入近乎為零，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的點撚知道？"},{"pid":"5b0c98c6802c0b858459111db59f4db467712a0b","tid":1544253,"uid":229793,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />媽的貢丸"},{"pid":"d27505af79b284b9ca4f2c30067cf650bdb04116","tid":1544253,"uid":202580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:21:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"61bbaa70be6c86b863acc4350afd0b5d34dad018","tid":1544253,"uid":147916,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:21:35.000Z","msg":"睇咁多次都咁好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fdc1763f9c8317a7aa768f6d34807878b3c115","tid":1544253,"uid":53666,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:22:09.000Z","msg":"屌你老母好撚好笑。 100/10"},{"pid":"8cddbb843c53230b3f85c6738b5d0cb6c9f74759","tid":1544253,"uid":207077,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZSnF9oK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZSnF9oK.gif&h=e1452aaf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b571e5945b7bfe4af3c94e525173b329f82c63d","tid":1544253,"uid":59305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:23:03.000Z","msg"